*JO:* Yeah, I mean, it=E2=80=99s like Aeroflot, right? They had the TU144s =
for flying supersonic mail for the Soviet government from one end of the So=
viet Union to the other. It works in that way, but that=E2=80=99s not the w=
orld we live in when it comes to developing an airline.

